---
By: Rainer Maria Rilke
Source:
  ID: 631057a1-0221-4885-ba61-78b661b62b70
  Source:
    Title: The Book of Hours
    Locus: I 44
Title: Leaving Paradise
Description: October 15
Format: Verse
---
Be our refuge from the wrath
that drove us out of Paradise.

Be our shepherd, but never call us --
we can't bear to know what's ahead.
